{"content":[{"attrs":{"alt":"","caption":"","src":"/demo/webinars/air-company-zerotrust.webp"},"type":"image"},{"attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"text":"【5/29（木）開催】ウェビナー「今さら聞けないゼロトラストのはじめかた」","type":"text"}],"type":"heading"},{"content":[{"text":"クラウド利用が進む今、企業の情報セキュリティ対策として「ゼロトラスト」は避けて通れないキーワードです。","type":"text"},{"type":"hardBreak"},{"text":"本ウェビナーでは、ゼロトラストの基礎から導入の進め方、具体的な活用方法まで、わかりやすく解説します。","type":"text"},{"type":"hardBreak"},{"text":"また、生成AI / MCPをフル活用し、自律型セキュリティ運用を実現する新製品、QueryPie Secure Enterprise AI Hub（仮称）、の情報を先行してお届けします。","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"text":"【ウェビナー概要】","type":"text"}],"type":"heading"},{"content":[{"content":[{"content":[{"text":"日時：2025年5月29日（木）13:00〜13:30","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"listItem"},{"content":[{"content":[{"text":"形式：Zoomによるオンライン開催","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"listItem"},{"content":[{"content":[{"text":"参加費：無料（事前登録制）","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"listItem"},{"content":[{"content":[{"text":"主催：AIR Company Limited","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"listItem"},{"content":[{"content":[{"text":"共催：QueryPie","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"listItem"}],"type":"bulletList"},{"attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"text":"【参加者特典】","type":"text"}],"type":"heading"},{"content":[{"text":"QueryPieの導入事例レポート（実際の構成図付き）をプレゼント！","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"text":"【講師】","type":"text"}],"type":"heading"},{"content":[{"text":"高橋 良汰（AIR社 データソリューション事業部）","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"text":"【詳細・お申し込みはこちら】","type":"text"}],"type":"heading"},{"content":[{"marks":[{"attrs":{"href":"https://air.co.jp/cat_02/12602/"},"type":"link"}],"text":"https://air.co.jp/cat_02/12602/","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"doc"}